# SkillWise AI Tutor - Environment Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values

# =============================================================================
# OPENAI CONFIGURATION (Required for AI Features)
# =============================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# EMAIL CONFIGURATION (Required for Password Reset & Notifications)
# =============================================================================
# Gmail Configuration (recommended):
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your-gmail-app-password

# For Gmail App Password setup:
# 1. Go to Google Account settings
# 2. Security > 2-Step Verification
# 3. App passwords > Generate app password
# 4. Use the generated password (not your regular Gmail password)

# =============================================================================
# MONITORING (Optional)
# =============================================================================
# Sentry for error tracking: https://sentry.io/
SENTRY_DSN=your-sentry-dsn-url

# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================
# - Database, Redis, and other core services are configured in docker-compose.yml
# - JWT secrets and other security keys are set to development defaults
# - For production deployment, all security keys must be changed
# - Most features work without these environment variables
# - Only AI features require OpenAI API key
# - Only password reset requires email configuration